---
description: Constrains the model's response to a JSON schema (referenced by path).
vars:
  - name: schema_path
    type: path
    description: Path (relative to the application) to the JSON schema the response must conform to.
  - name: strict
    type: bool
    description: If true, the response must be JSON only — no prose.
    default: true
    required: false
---
## Output format

Respond with valid JSON conforming to the schema at `{{ schema_path }}`.

{% if strict %}
Do not include any prose, comments, or markdown before or after the JSON.
The entire response must be parseable JSON.
{% else %}
You may include brief explanatory prose, but the primary payload must be
valid JSON conforming to the schema.
{% endif %}
